copy:
Congratulations! You've reached the end of the tutorials... for now. Ractive has a few more tricks up its sleeve, and we're working on creating more tutorials for them.

In the meantime, if you have questions about how to use Ractive, here are a few places to get help:

  • StackOverflow
  • The Ractive.js mailing list
  • GitHub issues
  • @RactiveJS on Twitter

If you've noticed any mistakes or bugs, come and let us know on the learn.ractivejs.org GitHub repo. Thanks!
